response.original_title: Makybe Diva - The Diva: A Champion Becomes a Legend
response.overview: Makybe Diva was a wonder mare, winning almost every prestigious group race on the Australian calendar - Sydney Cup, Australian Cup, BMW Classic, Cox Plate, Turnbull Stakes, Memsie Stakes, Queen Elizabeth Stakes and of course the 3 consecutive Melbourne Cups.
response.title: Makybe Diva - The Diva: A Champion Becomes a Legend
